international bureau of weights and meas.data-term: international bureau of weights and measures

examples.en: The tree is about two meters in girth.
Feet and meters are units of length.
The box has a volume of three cubic meters.
The company has 1000 square meters of storage.
The volume of the container is 100 cubic meters.
The adult animals reach a maximum length of two meters.
The residents of the neighborhood tussled with city hall for years about the broken parking meters.
